      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model (bilinear isotropic hardening Ti-6Al-4V) validated against coupon tensile data; geometric idealisation of thread profile justified by sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening parameters for Ti-6Al-4V (E=114 GPa, sigma_y=880 MPa, E_t=1.2 GPa) derived from supplier material certification coupon data. Sensitivity analysis shows thread-root geometry simplification introduces <1.5% change in predicted yield force. Gradation 3 achieved for model form."
