      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus sourced from lot-specific tensile coupon certificates accompanying the N=11 test constructs. Critical dimensions (rod diameter, screw outer diameter, inter-screw distance) measured by CMM on each specimen. Monte Carlo uncertainty propagation (n=1000) quantifies combined input uncertainty contribution to each QoI. Gradation 3 satisfied."
