      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6; Lab B: n=5). All specimens drawn from a single production lot; CMM dimensional inspection confirms compliance with design nominal. Inter-laboratory reproducibility coefficient <4%. Gradation 3 achieved, exceeding the required level."
