      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably matched to as-tested specimen parameters; traceability matrix provided.",
      "rationale": "Traceability matrix maps each FEA model input to its measured or certified source value for each of the 11 specimens. Boundary conditions replicate F1717 fixture constraints (fixed inferior block, axial-compressive displacement applied at superior block centroid at 5° from vertical). Equivalency confirmed at Gradation 2."
