      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.41), and F@40mm (1.09). All values below 1.96 threshold. Mean relative errors: stiffness 4.2%, yield force 6.8%, F@40mm 5.1%. All within the pre-established <10% bound. Gradation 3 achieved."
