      "rationale": "Construct stiffness is directly related to load-sharing behaviour at the fusion segment. Yield force and F@40mm are the primary acceptance endpoints in ASTM F1717 and the FDA guidance for spinal systems. Linkage between QoIs and clinical failure modes (screw fracture, rod fracture, loss of fixation) is documented in the Simulation Plan. Gradation 3 satisfied."
